text: Bjuråkers GIF is a sports club in Bjuråker, Sweden. It was established on 26 November 1952. The women's soccer team played in the Swedish top division in 1978. ==References== ==Other websites== *Soccer *Skiing Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Ice hockey teams in Sweden Category:1952 establishments in Europe Category:Ski clubs in Sweden Category:1950s establishments in Sweden
